            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Iucundus <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> Terenti <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertus</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>pecuarius <lb n="4"/>praeteriens quicum<lb break="no" n="5"/>que legis consiste <lb n="6"/>viator et vide quam in<lb break="no" n="7"/>digne raptus inane <lb n="8"/>querar vivere non <lb n="9"/>potui plures XXX per <lb n="10"/>annos nam erupuit <note>sic</note> se<lb break="no" n="11"/>rvos <note>sic</note> mihi vitam et ipse <lb n="12"/>praecipitem sesse <note>sic</note> deie<lb break="no" n="13"/>cit in amnem apstulit <note>sic</note> <lb n="14"/>huic Moenus quod <lb n="15"/>domino eripuit <lb n="16"/>patronus de suo posuit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Autopsie R. Wiegels. Unterhalb des Inschriftfeldes Bildfeld mit Hirtenszene. Z. 16 (Ende): IT steht auf dem Rahmen. Metrik: Z. 4-15: elegische Distichen.</p>
            </div>
